'''艾利森山大学'''（或稱'''蒙特埃里森大学'''；[[英文|英文]]：'''{{lang|en|Mount Allison University}}'''）是一所坐落于[[加拿大|加拿大]]东部[[新不伦瑞克|新不伦瑞克]]省和[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]省交界处{{tsl|en|Sackville, New Brunswick|萨克威尔镇}}的公立[[文理学院|文理学院]]型[[大学|大学]]，临近[[蒙克顿|蒙克顿]]市。该校创建于1839年，多次在加拿大[[麦克林|麦克林杂志]]基础本科类院校中排名第一 <ref>[http://oncampus.macleans.ca/education/2013/10/31/2014-university-rankings-primarily-undergraduate-results/ "2014 University Rankings: Primarily Undergraduate results"] {{Wayback|url=http://oncampus.macleans.ca/education/2013/10/31/2014-university-rankings-primarily-undergraduate-results/ |date=20140209091131 }}  Macleans.ca 2013年10月31日</ref><ref>[http://www.macleans.ca/education/university-rankings/primarily-undergraduate-universities/ "University Rankings 2018: Canada’s top Primarily Undergraduate schools"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.macleans.ca/education/university-rankings/primarily-undergraduate-universities/ |date=20191102053227 }} Macleans.ca 2017年10月11日</ref>。

== 简史 ==
艾利森山大学的起源可以追溯到1839年一个由当地商人{{tsl|en|Charles Frederick Allison|查尔斯·艾利森}}创立的文理学院，1854年该校又成立了女子学院。1858年，新不伦瑞克省政府正式授予该校颁发本科学位的资格，艾利森山学院于1859年正式成立<ref name="gutenberg.org">https://www.gutenberg.org/files/32699/32699-h/32699-h.htm {{Wayback|url=https://www.gutenberg.org/files/32699/32699-h/32699-h.htm |date=20160303215607 }} The Project Gutenberg EBook of The Makers of Canada: Index and Dictionary of Canadian History, by Various 2010</ref>。大学于1875年成为加拿大第一所授予女性学生学位的院校。校刊"The Argosy"创立于1872年，是全加拿大历史最悠久的学生出版物之一<ref>[http://argosy.ca/about-argosy "About The Argosy"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104235613/http://argosy.ca/about-argosy |date=2013-11-04 }} argosy.ca </ref>。截至2013年，该校有54位毕业生成为[[罗德学者|罗德学者]]<ref>[http://www.mta.ca/Community/News/2014/December_2014/Bernard_Soubry_named_Mount_Allison%E2%80%99s_53rd_Rhodes_Scholar/   Bernard Soubry named Mount Allison’s 53rd Rhodes Scholar] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mta.ca/Community/News/2014/December_2014/Bernard_Soubry_named_Mount_Allison%E2%80%99s_53rd_Rhodes_Scholar/ |date=20190614172136 }} Mount Allison University 2014年12月1日</ref><ref>[http://www.mta.ca/Community/News/2013/December/Kylie_de_Chastelain_is_Mount_Allison_University%E2%80%99s_52nd_Rhodes_Scholar!/  Kylie de Chastelain is Mount Allison University’s 52nd Rhodes Scholar!] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mta.ca/Community/News/2013/December/Kylie_de_Chastelain_is_Mount_Allison_University%E2%80%99s_52nd_Rhodes_Scholar!/ |date=20190630044340 }} Mount Allison University 2013年12月2日</ref><ref>[http://www.mta.ca/news/index.php?id=4004 Caroline Whidden is Mount Allison’s 51st Rhodes Scholar"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130408165743/http://www.mta.ca/news/index.php?id=4004 |date=2013-04-08 }} Mount Allison University 2012年11月27日 </ref><ref>[http://www.rhodeshouse.ox.ac.uk/rhodes-scholars-elect-class-of-2013/caroline-whidden Caroline Whidden] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029204405/http://www.rhodeshouse.ox.ac.uk/rhodes-scholars-elect-class-of-2013/caroline-whidden |date=2013-10-29 }} The Rhodes Scholarships </ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mta.ca/Community/News/2017/November/Colin_Robertson_is_Mount_Allison%E2%80%99s_54th_Rhodes_Scholar/ |title="Colin Robertson is Mount Allison's 54th Rhodes Scholar" |access-date=2022-03-26 |archive-date=2019-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612144716/https://mta.ca/Community/News/2017/November/Colin_Robertson_is_Mount_Allison%E2%80%99s_54th_Rhodes_Scholar/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[加拿大广播公司|加拿大广播公司]]著名主持人{{tsl|en|Peter Mansbridge|彼得·曼斯布里奇}}在退休前曾为大学[[校监|校监]]<ref>[http://www.mta.ca/news/index.php?id=2208 "Mount Allison University appoints Peter Mansbridge as Chancellor"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130606140840/http://www.mta.ca/news/index.php?id=2208 |date=2013-06-06 }} Mount Allison University 2009年11月09日 </ref>。

== 基本信息 ==
目前该校占地约77英亩<ref>[http://www.mta.ca/apply-www/whymta/history.html  History and Facts] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20131116054319/http://www.mta.ca/apply-www/whymta/history.html |date=2013-11-16 }} Mount Allison University</ref>，在校学生约有2,200名<ref>[http://www.atlanticuniversities.ca/system/files/documents/AAUFactsFiguresEnrolments/Full%20Time%20plus%20Part%20Time%202012.pdf  Full Time plus Part Time 2012] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430111806/http://www.atlanticuniversities.ca/system/files/documents/AAUFactsFiguresEnrolments/Full%20Time%20plus%20Part%20Time%202012.pdf |date=2013-04-30 }} Association of Atlantic Universities  2012年10月15日</ref>，设立人文学院(Faculty of Arts)、理学院(Faculty of Science)和社会科学院(Faculty of Social Science)，提供[[文学士|文学士]]、[[理学士|理学士]]、商学士、艺术学士和音乐学士五类[[学士|学士]]学位，以及[[生物|生物]]和[[化学|化学]]专业的[[理学硕士|理学硕士]]学位，

艾利森山大学是[[加拿大大西洋地区|加拿大大西洋地区]]的主要[[高等院校|高等院校]]之一，近年{{When|time=20201012}}有批评认为该校在学生就业准备方面的指导较差<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/education/canadian-university-report/canadian-university-report-2013-career-preparation---co-op-internship-and-other-work-related-opportunities/article4631565/ |title=加拿大环球邮报: Canadian University Report 2013: Career Preparation - Co-op, internship and other work-related opportunities |access-date=2016-11-28 |archive-date=2016-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128135901/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/education/canadian-university-report/canadian-university-report-2013-career-preparation---co-op-internship-and-other-work-related-opportunities/article4631565/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[美术|美术]]、[[航空|航空]]和[[认知科学|认知科学]]是艾利森山大学的特色专业<ref>[http://www.macleans.ca/schools/mount-allison-university/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.macleans.ca/schools/mount-allison-university/ |date=20210404190108 }} 麦克林: Mount Allison University]]</ref>，该校与{{tsl|en|Moncton Flight College|蒙克顿飞行学院}}共同授予[[航空科学|航空科学]]学士<ref>[http://www.mta.ca/academic_calendar/part3.html "Academic Degrees, Programs and Courses"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mta.ca/academic_calendar/part3.html |date=20210414081548 }} Mount Allison University 2013年4月1日</ref>。该校也与加拿大东部的其它三所文理学院[[阿卡迪亚大学|阿卡迪亚大学]]、[[主教大学|主教大学]]、{{le|圣弗朗西斯·格扎维埃大学|St. Francis Xavier University}}合称枫叶大学联盟<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mapleleague.ca/ |title=枫叶大学联盟官网 |access-date=2022-03-26 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225195221/http://mapleleague.ca/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

